<title>Prayer for Help in Public Worship. ƲIT165</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Himak nitak fehna hoka
 Ʋbanumpa hanta
 Haklot il itʋnaha kʋt,
 Pi yukpa fehnʋshke.

[V2]
 Pi̱ki ʋba Chihowa ma!
 Auet pi̱ nukha̱klot
 Ish pi apelahanchi na,
 E chithaiyanashke.

[V3]
 Chishno ak bieka kak o̱
 Nitak moma hoka
 E chim antia hi ak o̱,
 Ish pi apelashke.

[V4]
 Shilombish Holitopa ya̱
 Himonasi pimʋt
 Ish pi apelahanchi na,
 Pi nuktaiyalashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Himak nitak fehna hoka</aka>
<author>George L. Williams</author>
<hymn_number>165</hymn_number>
</song>